<P><FONT SIZE=6 FACE="Arial"><B>About the Noam Chomsky Archive</B></FONT>

<P>New World Media and ZNet are proud to bring you a comprehensive collection of Chomsky's political work -- over
<FONT COLOR="#800000"><I>ten</I></FONT> megabytes of text and <FONT COLOR="#800000"><I>seven</I></FONT> hours of
audio! The <A HREF="http://www.lbbs.org/">ZNet</A> web site hosts <A HREF="http://www.lbbs.org/zmag/index.htm">Z
Magazine</A> and <A HREF="http://www.lbbs.org/sep/sep.htm">South End Press</A>, two major publishers of Chomsky's
work.

<P>We're constantly growing! More selections are on the way. Soon we will also offer search capabilities and a
system-wide index. Please <!--A HREF="/comment/comment2.htm"--><A HREF="mailto:chomskyarchive@yahoo.com">tell us what you
think</A> about the archive so far!
</CENTER>

